Setup:

  $ . $TESTDIR/setup.sh
  $ export HOME=$PWD
  $ printf 'a%.0s' {1..2000} > ignored
  $ printf '\n' >> ignored
  $ printf 'b%.0s' {1..200} >> ignored
  $ printf 'c%.0s' {1..1999} > not_ignored

Ignore the string of 2000 alphas.

  $ ag "aaaaaaa"
  [1]

Do not ignore the string of only 1999 charlies.

  $ ag "ccccccc"
  not_ignored:1:

Do not ignore the string of less than 2000 bravos even through they share a file
with 2000 alphas

  $ ag "bbbbbbb"
  ignored:2:bbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbb

Ignore the string of 200 charlies if we shorten the acceptable line length.

  $ ag --long-line-length 100 "cccccccc"
  [1]
